title: 11/21 Fantasy Football Podcast: Waiver Wire; Stash Rodgers & Johnson?
description:
We've got the names you need to know as you make your waiver claims tonight! Our priorities at QB (10:14) including Andy Dalton and Tyrod Taylor, RB (12:00) including Devontae Booker and a number of players who are widely-owned but could be available in your leagues, WR (18:00) including a couple of Redskins and Corey Coleman, TE (21:54) including Charles Clay and DSTs (24:45) ... Recapping ATL-SEA (27:30) and PHI-DAL (33:10). Are Dez Bryant and Julio Jones still must-starts? ... Dropometer (42:40) and then a deeper look at the Waiver Wire (46:20) including QBs with good playoff matchups (51:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
